rComments: Very competent and helpful. Can be sarcastic.

Martina was the best language teacher I've ever had. Her class was always fun, even tough it was early morning. We never had to worry about grades in this class, because Martina always prepared us well for tests and assignments. If we didn't understand something, she'd always explain it to us (in english if necessary).
She is an awesome instructor, no one would deny that. However, the fact that it took her an entire semester to return assignments is totally unacceptable.
great instructor: funny and attentive to students' concerns.
SUPER TEACHER!!!! Whoever gets her next year is extremely lucky!
She is very kind and fare, and is able to make the language learning fun and engaging. Wunderbar!
Excellent at engaging students and encouraging participation. Some may not appreciate her sense of humour. Great instructor.
